*(Optional: Upload a screenshot named `dashboard.png` showing your Excel dashboard)*  

---

## 🚀 How to Use
1. Download `sales_data.xlsx`.  
2. Open in Microsoft Excel (2016 or later recommended).  
3. Explore Pivot Tables and Dashboard sheets.  

